OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781543961
OL,3,COil tank and asbestos among fly-tipped
OL,4,Crubbish on emergency route
OL,6,FAn oil tank, asbestos sheeting and a
OL,7,Fsofa are among fly-tipped rubbish
OL,8,Fblocking an emergency access route to
OL,9,Fthe M5 motorway in Devon.
OL,11,FNational Highways say they believe the
OL,12,Fdumping happened on two separate
OL,13,Foccasions at Little Copse, between
OL,14,FCullompton and Honiton.
OL,16,FThe road is used to release traffic
OL,17,Ftrapped between junctions 28 and 29
OL,18,Fwhen there is an incident on the
OL,19,Fmotorway.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
