OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781543961
OL,3,COil tank and asbestos among fly-tipped
OL,4,Crubbish on emergency route
OL,6,FThe rubbish includes an oil central
OL,7,Fheating tank, oil drum, asbestos
OL,8,Fsheeting, a sofa and other furniture.
OL,10,FMid Devon District Council said it
OL,11,Fwill cost more than #4,500 to remove
OL,12,Fand dispose of.
OL,14,FThe emergency turning point at Little
OL,15,FCopse can be accessed via a police
OL,16,Fviewing platform on the southbound
OL,17,Fcarriageway, opening on to the B3181,
OL,18,Fbut has been out of action due to the
OL,19,Fblockage.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781543961
OL,3,COil tank and asbestos among fly-tipped
OL,4,Crubbish on emergency route
OL,6,FEmma Bazeley, National Highways
OL,7,Fmaintenance service manager for the
OL,8,FSouth West, said: "The items look like
OL,9,Fthey've come from a house clearance
OL,10,Fand anyone who's paid a company to
OL,11,Fdispose of their rubbish appropriately
OL,12,Fmay well recognise them.
OL,14,F"If anyone does recognise the items,
OL,15,Fthey can get in touch with us and we
OL,16,Fcan notify the relevant authorities.
OL,26,@pD@SOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781543961
OL,3,COil tank and asbestos among fly-tipped
OL,4,Crubbish on emergency route
OL,6,F"It's totally irresponsible to do
OL,7,Fthis, they've not only put ours and
OL,8,Fpolice operations at risk but it can
OL,9,Fpose a risk to wildlife and the
OL,10,Fenvironment and it's costly to remove.
OL,12,F"Clearing litter from our roads costs
OL,13,Fthe taxpayer millions of pounds a
OL,14,Fyear, and it's a cost local
OL,15,Fauthorities can ill afford."
OL,17,FThe access gate from the motorway is
OL,18,Flocked but those responsible for the
OL,19,Ffly-tipping have managed to gain
OL,20,Faccess to the site via a gate
OL,21,Falongside the B3181.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781543961
OL,3,COil tank and asbestos among fly-tipped
OL,4,Crubbish on emergency route
OL,6,FNational Highways said their officers
OL,7,Fand police have been unable to use the
OL,8,Femergency access road since the
OL,9,Fblockage was discovered.
OL,11,FIn the meantime the company has
OL,12,Fsecurely locked the second access
OL,13,Fgate, cleared vegetation obscuring
OL,14,Fviews and liaised with the council to
OL,15,Fclear the debris.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781543961
OL,3,COil tank and asbestos among fly-tipped
OL,4,Crubbish on emergency route
OL,6,FCouncillor Josh Wright, Mid Devon
OL,7,FDistrict Council's cabinet member for
OL,8,Fservice delivery and continuous
OL,9,Fimprovement said: "It's incredibly
OL,10,Ffrustrating to see fly-tipping on this
OL,11,Fscale, particularly somewhere so
OL,12,Fimportant.
OL,14,F"As well as harming the environment,
OL,15,Fit's costly to clear up and has caused
OL,16,Fdisruption to an emergency access
OL,17,Froute which could have serious
OL,18,Fconsequences if access is needed
OL,19,Fduring an incident.
OL,26,@qD@SOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781543961
OL,3,COil tank and asbestos among fly-tipped
OL,4,Crubbish on emergency route
OL,6,F"Our teams are working with partners
OL,7,Fto get the site cleared as quickly and
OL,8,Fsafely as possible. We'd ask anyone
OL,9,Fwith information to come forward and
OL,10,Fremind people to always check anyone
OL,11,Ftaking away waste is licensed to
OL,12,Fdispose of it properly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
